    <li><a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/dc-md-va/2026/06/16/dca-flights-be-halted-parts-july-3-july-4/">The Washington Post: DCA flights to be halted for parts of July 3 and July 4</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://wjla.com/news/local/heres-when-dcas-reagan-national-airport-runways-will-be-closed-and-flights-delayed-for-july-4-america-250-events-june-2026">WJLA: DCA runway closures and flight delays for America 250 events</a></li>
